                  <summary>Five Pillars of Mystery, አምስቱ፡ አዕማደ፡ ምሥጢር፡ (f<locus target="#1r"/>-60v); The Faith of the 318 Fathers (Commentary on the Nicaean Creed, ትርጓሜ: ጸሎተ: ሃይማኖት:) (f<locus target="#60v"/>-104r); Image of the Trinity, Mälk‘a Śǝllase, መልክአ፡ ሥላሴ፡. Chaîne, Répertoire 20; MG59 189ff. (f<locus target="#105r"/>-116r); List of the names of Heretics, አስማቲሆሙ: ለመናፍቃን: (f<locus target="#116r"/>-119v)</summary>
